                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ذَلُولاً﴾ سَهْلَةً، مُمَهَّدَةً تَسْتَقِرُّونَ عَلَيْهَا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿مَنَاكِبِهَا﴾ نَوَاحِيهَا، وَجَوَانِبِهَا.</h2>\n<p>﴿وَإِلَيْهِ النُّشُورُ﴾ إِلَيْهِ تُبْعَثُونَ مِنْ قُبُورِكُمْ لِلْجَزَاءِ وَالحِسَابِ.</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "67:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مَنْ فِي السَّمَاءِ﴾ اللهَ الَّذِي فِي العُلُوِّ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿تَمُورُ﴾ تَضْطَرِبُ بِكُمْ حَتَّى تَهْلِكُوا.</h2>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "67:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿حَاصِبًا﴾ رِيحًا تَرْجُمُكُمْ بِالحِجَارَةِ الصَّغِيرَةِ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿نَذِيرِ﴾ تَحْذِيرِي لَكُمْ.</h2>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "67:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿نَكِيرِ﴾ إِنْكَارِي عَلَيْهِمْ، وَتَغْيِيرُ مَا بِهِمْ مِنَ النِّعْمَةِ.</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "67:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿صَآفَّاتٍ﴾ بَاسِطَاتٍ أَجْنِحَتَهَا عِنْدَ طَيَرَانِهَا فِي الهَوَاءِ.</p>\n<h2>﴿وَيَقْبِضْنَ﴾ يَضْمُمْنَهَا إِلَى جُنُوبِهَا أَحْيانَا.</h2>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "67:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿غُرُورٍ﴾ خِدَاعٍ وَضَلاَلٍ مِنَ الشَّيْطَانِ.</h2>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "67:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿لَجُّوا﴾ اسْتَمَرُّوا، وَتَمَادَوْا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿عُتُوٍّ﴾ مُعَانَدَةٍ، وَاسْتِكْبَارٍ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿وَنُفُورٍ﴾ شُرُودٍ وَتَبَاعُدٍ عَنِ الحَقِّ.</h2>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "67:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 116,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_wordmeanings",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Wordmeanings",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿مُكِبًّا﴾ مُنَكَّسًا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿سَوِيًّا﴾ مُسْتَوِيًا، مُنْتَصِبَ القَامَةِ سَالِمًا.</h2>\n<h2>﴿صِرَاطٍ مُسْتَقِيمٍ﴾ طَرِيقٍ وَاضِحٍ لاَ اعْوِجَاجَ فِيهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
